<% title "Rider Registration" %>

  <h2 class="text-center">Join us in Rangely Colorado  <br /> <%= Time.current.year+1 %> Rangely OHV Adventure Rally.</h2>
  <p>&nbsp;</p>

  <p>Registration is now
  <% if @date == @roar_closed  %>
    closed. You must register at the event.
  <% else %>
    open online through May 1st, after that you may register at the event.
  <% end %>
  </p>

  <p>Registration includes an event t-shirt, guided rides (optional), breakfast on Friday and Saturday, dinner on Friday and all events listed
  in the schedule, unless noted. Sack lunches for Friday and Saturday can be ordered on the registration form at an additional charge.</p>

