      <ul>
        <li>Each buggy is $65</li>
        <li>Includes one t-shirt and a goody bag</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <p><strong>After April 25th:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Each buggy is $70</li>
        <li>Includes one t-shirt and a goody bag <span class="text-danger text-small">*</span></li>
      </ul>
      <span class="text-danger">* T-Shirt is not guaranteed. Based on availablity</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>&nbsp;</p>

